{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"俺は布団の間からウィスキーを取り出す。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00112",
linknext="block_00114",
},
block_00114={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000128",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「ほ、本当に酒用意してたんですか？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00113",
linknext="block_00115",
},
block_00115={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000562",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「ああ、秘蔵の酒でな。アメリカにいた時に買ったんだよ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00114",
linknext="block_00116",
},
block_00116={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000129",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「でも、これ日本のウィスキーですよね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00115",
linknext="block_00117",
},
block_00117={
{"bg",file="ev_com_g05_02",sync=0,face=1,time=400,path=":ev/ev_com_g05/",set="ev_com_g05"},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000563",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「ああ、そうだ。地球の裏側で売られていた日本の酒、だから俺はそれを買った」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00116",
linknext="block_00118",
},
block_00118={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000564",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「当時は思ったよ。高かったしな。",
{"rt2"},
"こいつは、最高の瞬間に開けようって、な」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00117",
linknext="block_00119",
},
block_00119={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000130",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「でも、開いてませんね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00118",
linknext="block_00120",
},
block_00120={
{"bg",file="ev_com_g05_01",sync=0,face=1,time=400,path=":ev/ev_com_g05/",set="ev_com_g05"},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000565",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「当たり前だよ。最高って言うのはいつだって、後から分かるもんさ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00119",
linknext="block_00121",
},
block_00121={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000131",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「最高な瞬間は……後から分かる……ですか」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00120",
linknext="block_00122",
},
block_00122={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000566",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「そういう事だ。最高な瞬間ってヤツはつかまえるのが難しい」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00121",
linknext="block_00123",
},
block_00123={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000567",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「後から考えれば、最高と思えた瞬間は、何度もあったさ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00122",
linknext="block_00124",
},
block_00124={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000568",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「俺は恵まれてたからな……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00123",
linknext="block_00125",
},
block_00125={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000132",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「恵まれてた……ですか。まぁ、普通の人なら健一郎さんの人生は波瀾万丈すぎて、そんな事は言えないでしょうけどね」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00124",
linknext="block_00126",
},
block_00126={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000569",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「かもな」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00125",
linknext="block_00127",
},
block_00127={
{"bg",file="ev_com_g05_02",sync=0,face=1,time=400,path=":ev/ev_com_g05/",set="ev_com_g05"},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000570",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「でもさ。あったんだよ。人生最高の瞬間ってやつは」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00126",
linknext="block_00128",
},
block_00128={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000571",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「だからさ、今こそ開けるんだよ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00127",
linknext="block_00129",
},
block_00129={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000133",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「今？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00128",
linknext="block_00130",
},
block_00130={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000572",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「ああ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00129",
linknext="block_00131",
},
block_00131={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000573",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「つきあってくれるか？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00130",
linknext="block_00132",
},
block_00132={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wkd_000134",ch="wkd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"若田"},
"「……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00131",
linknext="block_00133",
},
block_00133={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"若田は小さく頷く。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00132",
linknext="block_00134",
},
block_00134={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"幸福は仮象の春色一面の空の様なものだ。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00133",
linknext="block_00135",
},
block_00135={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"まるで、本体などなく、なにかの拍子に、きらきらと立ち現れる、色彩過多の電燈群の様。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00134",
linknext="block_00136",
},
block_00136={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"あの日、見た桜と一人の少女。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00135",
linknext="block_00137",
},
block_00137={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"あの風景は、私を追い越して、何処かへ行ったのか？",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00136",
linknext="block_00138",
},
block_00138={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"それとも、俺が何処かに、置き忘れてしまったのか？",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00137",
linknext="block_00139",
},
block_00139={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"七つの苦しみと、七つの幸福。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00138",
linknext="block_00140",
},
block_00140={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"それらの間で、俺たちは揺れ動く。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00139",
linknext="block_00141",
},
block_00141={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"まるで振り子の様だ。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00140",
linknext="block_00142",
},
block_00142={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"だから――",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00141",
linknext="block_00143",
},
block_00143={
{"bg",file="ev_com_g05_01",path=":ev/ev_com_g05/",set="ev_com_g05"},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000574",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「笑って乾杯してくれや」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00142",
linknext="block_00144",
},
block_00144={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000575",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「俺のここまでの人生に」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00143",
linknext="block_00145",
},
block_00145={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_kid_000576",ch="kid"},
},
ja={
{
name={"健一郎"},
"「これからの幸福の瞬間に」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00144",
linknext="block_00146",
},
